<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٨٩١ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/118">إِبْرَاهِيمُ بْنُ مُوسَى: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6707">هِشَامٌ </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4035">ابْنَ جُرَيْجٍ </a>أَخْبَرَهُمْ: قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4385">عَطَاءٌ </a>: قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرٌ </a>: <span class="c2">«أَنَا وَأَبِي وَخَالِي مِنْ أَصْحَابِ الْعَقَبَةِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>